      {
        "id": "29bcd452-3db7-4425-a710-4cb1cbc5fc0c",
        "title": "Lesson 4-1",
        "type": "rich",
        "order_index": 1,
        "content": {
          "type": "doc",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Subtitle: 〜欲さん (want/wish/would like to~)"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "You might be thinking at this point. Wait... shouldn't this verb be used further back in the course and not at the intermediate level? However, this word is actually unique compared to any other language."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "In most languages, verbs such as \"want\", \"wish\", \"would like\" is a VERB."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "HOWEVER, in Okinawan, it is an ADJECTIVE."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "欲さん can also be 欲しゃん (due to the s/sh merger, explanation in a different lesson)."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "In Lower Intermediate 2, we learned that to negate an informal adjective, we substitute the -san with a -koo neen."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Let's practice."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Translate the following from English to Okinawan. (Informal = 1/5 formal)."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "English:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bulletList",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "attrs": {
                        "textAlign": null
                      },
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "I want to learn Okinawan [i.e., the language]."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "attrs": {
                        "textAlign": null
                      },
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "I do not want to go to the ocean/sea."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "attrs": {
                        "textAlign": null
                      },
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "I would like to drink coffee."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Okinawan:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bulletList",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "attrs": {
                        "textAlign": null
                      },
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "沖縄語 習（なら）い欲（ぶ）さん。"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "2."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
