                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Subtitle: 〜（や）くとぅ (because) Review"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Let's translate 4:22-4:27 of the following video. You should be able to translate it based on what we covered so far (so there will be no answer key for this). Good luck! うぬ前（めー）からやがや？"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "今（なま）いくち なとーが すら 分（わ）からんくとぅ 。"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
